x4freetext: A 550 microg/cm 238UF4 target evaporated on a carbon
fission-fragment counters. Two telescopes, each of
them consisting of 150- and 1000-microm dE surface
barrier Si counters and a 10-cm NaI(Tl) E counter.
fragments have been measured in coincidence with
light charged particles for 64, 129, 199, and 269 MeV
